Program: Outlook
Title: Who Runs Your World?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrtl
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look back at the Outlook series on the results of a global survey commissioned by the World Service in which 50,000 people were asked who rules their world. It looks at panchayati raj and village councils, religious leaders, landowners and marriage. Presenter: Heather Payton.